# Animation Overhaul — Emil Kowalski Design Engineering Principles

Implementasi prinsip animasi dari [Emil Kowalski's Design Engineering Skill](https://github.com/emilkowalski/skill) dan [animations.dev](https://animations.dev/) ke seluruh halaman iDesk. Saat ini animasi bersifat basic (CSS utilities sederhana, `transition-all` di 105 file, easing curve lemah). Goal: animasi yang **feel right** — responsive, performant, dan premium.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope besar** — 105 file menggunakan `transition-all` (anti-pattern). Implementasi dilakukan bertahap per phase untuk meminimalkan risiko regresi.

> [!WARNING]
> **`transition-all` → specific properties** akan mengubah banyak hover/interaction behavior. Beberapa edge case mungkin perlu fine-tuning manual.

---

## Audit Findings (Emil Kowalski Principles)

### Masalah Yang Ditemukan

| # | Issue | Severity | Count | Emil's Rule |
|---|-------|----------|-------|-------------|
| 1 | `transition-all` digunakan di mana-mana | 🔴 High | **105 files** | "Specify exact properties; avoid `all`" |
| 2 | `ease-in` pada exit page transition | 🔴 High | BentoLayout L31 | "Never use ease-in for UI animations" |
| 3 | CSS `easeOut`/`easeIn` bawaan (terlalu lemah) | 🟡 Medium | Semua transitions | "Use custom easing curves — built-in CSS easings are too weak" |
| 4 | `animate-fade-in-up` tanpa definisi keyframe | 🟡 Medium | 24 files | Utility CSS tanpa keyframe = no animation |
| 5 | No `prefers-reduced-motion` support | 🟡 Medium | Global | "Reduced motion means fewer animations, not zero" |
| 6 | Stagger delay 0.4s terlalu lama | 🟠 Low | StaggerList | "Keep stagger delays short (30-80ms)" |
| 7 | AnimatedCounter linear (bukan eased) | 🟠 Low | animated.tsx | Counter should use eased timing |
| 8 | No active/press states pada buttons | 🟡 Medium | Semua buttons | "Buttons must feel responsive to press" |
| 9 | Page transition hanya opacity (no subtle y) | 🟠 Low | BentoLayout | Enter should have subtle translateY |
| 10 | ZoomCalendar minimal animation | 🟡 Medium | 1 animate class | Hampir tidak ada animation |
| 11 | TicketList no list enter animation | 🟡 Medium | 7 animate refs | Data list tanpa stagger enter |
| 12 | No exit animations on dynamic content | 🟡 Medium | Semua halaman | "Nothing disappears instantly" |

