## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Foundation — Animation System & CSS Variables (Core)

Membangun sistem animasi yang konsisten sebagai foundation untuk semua halaman.

---

#### [MODIFY] [index.css](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/index.css)

**Tambah CSS custom properties & keyframes:**

```css
:root {
  /* Emil Kowalski recommended easing curves */
  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
  --ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1);
  --ease-out-back: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  --ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1.2, 0.36, 1);
}

/* Keyframes for animate-fade-in-up (currently undefined!) */
@keyframes fade-in-up { ... }
@keyframes fade-in-down { ... }
@keyframes scale-in { ... }
@keyframes slide-in-right { ... }

/* Reduced motion support */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.15s !important;
  }
}

/* Button press feedback (global) */
button:active, [role="button"]:active {
  transform: scale(0.97);
}
```

---

#### [MODIFY] [tailwind.config.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/tailwind.config.ts)

Tambah custom animation utilities di Tailwind extend:
- `fade-in-up`, `fade-in-down`, `scale-in`, `slide-in-right`, `slide-in-left`, `pop-in`
