### Phase 2: Core Components — Animation Primitives

Upgrade komponen animasi shared yang dipakai di mana-mana.

---

#### [MODIFY] [BentoLayout.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/components/layout/BentoLayout.tsx)

| Before | After | Why |
|--------|-------|-----|
| `ease: 'easeOut'` (built-in lemah) | `ease: [0.23, 1, 0.32, 1]` (custom curve) | Built-in CSS easings lack punch |
| `ease: 'easeIn'` on exit | `ease: [0.23, 1, 0.32, 1]` with shorter duration | Never use ease-in for UI |
| `duration: 0.15` enter, `0.1` exit | `duration: 0.2` enter, `0.12` exit | Asymmetric: enter slightly longer |
| Opacity only | `opacity + translateY(8px)` enter | Subtle movement makes it feel alive |

---

#### [MODIFY] [animated.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/components/ui/animated.tsx)

| Before | After | Why |
|--------|-------|-----|
| CSS `animate-${animation}` (undefined) | Proper framer-motion integration | CSS keyframes are not defined |
| AnimatedCounter linear steps | Eased animation with `requestAnimationFrame` | Linear counting feels robotic |
| No exit animations | Exit support via AnimatePresence | Elements should not vanish |
| `staggerDelay = 0.05` as string calc | `staggerDelay = 0.04` (40ms) | 30-80ms range per Emil |

---

#### [MODIFY] [StaggerList.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/components/ui/StaggerList.tsx)

| Before | After | Why |
|--------|-------|-----|
| `ease: [0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1]` (weak) | `ease: [0.23, 1, 0.32, 1]` (strong ease-out) | Custom curve feels more intentional |
| `animationDuration = 0.4` (400ms!) | `animationDuration = 0.25` (250ms) | UI animations should stay under 300ms |
| `filter: 'blur(4px)'` on all items | `filter: 'blur(2px)'` subtle only | 4px blur is too heavy, distracting |
| `delayChildren: 0.1` (100ms wait) | `delayChildren: 0.05` (50ms) | Don't block interaction |

