### Phase 3: High-Traffic Pages — Dashboard, Tickets, Zoom

Upgrade animasi pada halaman yang paling sering diakses.

---

#### [MODIFY] [BentoDashboardPage.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/features/dashboard/pages/BentoDashboardPage.tsx)

**Masalah:** 28 animation refs tapi semuanya CSS utility basic (`transition-all`, `animate-fade-in-up`, `animate-pulse`).

| Before | After | Why |
|--------|-------|-----|
| `transition-all` pada stat cards | `transition: transform 200ms var(--ease-out), opacity 200ms var(--ease-out)` | Specify exact props |
| `animate-fade-in-up` tanpa keyframe | framer-motion stagger entry | Actually animate |
| `animate-pulse` pada live dot | Custom subtle pulse (scale 1→1.2→1) | animate-pulse is too aggressive |
| `transition-all` pada chart bars | `transition: transform 150ms var(--ease-out)` | Chart bars only scale on hover |
| No stagger on stat cards | Stagger 40ms delay between cards | Cascading feel |

