### Phase 4: Global `transition-all` Cleanup

Systematic replacement dari `transition-all` ke specific properties di 105 files.

**Strategy:** Batch replacement menggunakan pattern:

| Pattern | Replacement |
|---------|-------------|
| `transition-all` pada hover:bg, hover:text | `transition-colors` |
| `transition-all` pada hover:scale, transform | `transition-transform` |
| `transition-all` pada hover:opacity | `transition-opacity` |
| `transition-all` pada mixed hover | Specific: `transition: color 150ms, transform 150ms` |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Phase ini dilakukan incremental — mulai dari high-traffic pages (dashboard, tickets, zoom, login, notifications), kemudian sisanya. Setiap batch di-verify visual sebelum lanjut.

